## `admiral_list_lanes`

See all active sessions and their status

Lists every active lane with captain name, task status, and progress.

## `admiral_create_lane`

Create a new session/lane

Starts a new session for a project. Picks agents and creates the worktree.

## `admiral_steer_captain`

Send a message to a captain

Delivers a message to a specific captain. Use to give direction, approve work, or coordinate between lanes.

## `admiral_post_to_human`

Surface a message to the human

Posts to the human's activity feed. Only use for decisions that genuinely require human judgment. You are the buffer — handle what you can.

## `admiral_list_projects`

List registered projects

Shows all projects the system knows about.

## `read_file`

Read any file by absolute path

Read-only file access. You cannot edit files — go through a captain for that.

## `run_command`

Run a shell command

Execute a command with an absolute cwd path. Read-only — no destructive operations.

## `web_search`

Search the web

Search the web for documentation or information.
